    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>真的遍地都是坑，唉<br>稍后详细说明。</p><p><strong>数学公式</strong><br> $ a+b=c^2 $</p><a id="more"></a><p><a href="http://world.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2019/1105/MAIN201911052156000488028911555.JPG" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://world.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2019/1105/MAIN201911052156000488028911555.JPG</a></p><blockquote><p><strong>在主题中开启mathjax开关</strong><br>如何使用了主题了，别忘了在主题文件夹（Theme）中开启mathjax开关，下面以next主题为例，介绍下如何打开mathjax开关。<br>进入到主题目录，找到_config.yml配置问题，把mathjax默认的false修改为true，具体如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># MathJax Support</span><br><span class="line">mathjax:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  per_page: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>别着急，这样还不够，<strong>还需要在文章的Front-matter里打开mathjax开关</strong>，如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: index.html</span><br><span class="line">date: 2016-12-28 21:01:30</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">mathjax: true</span><br><span class="line">--</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>不要嫌麻烦，之所以要在文章头里设置开关，是因为考虑只有在用到公式的页面才加载 Mathjax，这样不需要渲染数学公式的页面的访问速度就不会受到影响了。</p></blockquote><p><img src="http://world.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2019/1105/MAIN201911052156000488028911555.JPG" alt="2015-06-01 151026"></p><h1 id="一级目录"><a href="#一级目录" class="headerlink" title="一级目录"></a>一级目录</h1><h2 id="1-1"><a href="#1-1" class="headerlink" title="1.1"></a>1.1</h2><h2 id="1-2"><a href="#1-2" class="headerlink" title="1.2"></a>1.2</h2><h2 id="二级目录"><a href="#二级目录" class="headerlink" title="二级目录"></a>二级目录</h2><h3 id="三级目录1-2-1"><a href="#三级目录1-2-1" class="headerlink" title="三级目录1.2.1"></a>三级目录1.2.1</h3><h3 id="三级目录"><a href="#三级目录" class="headerlink" title="三级目录"></a>三级目录</h3><h4 id="4"><a href="#4" class="headerlink" title="4"></a>4</h4><p>444</p><h5 id="5级"><a href="#5级" class="headerlink" title="5级"></a>5级</h5><p>555</p>]]></content>
    
